snippet.title: Miniclip: UFO Joe Gameplay
snippet.description:
Another old Miniclip flash game to go. This was where you would guild the orange dude in the ship to land on many different places in correct orders. Leave a like and a comment if you think you remember this throwback.

Platforms:
BlueMaxima's Flashpoint
Y8 Browser
------------------------------
By Bandicam Screen Recorder (https://www.bandicam.com)
